Programming procedure:
1. Switch IGN Off for 45 sec
2. Push service button 14 times to enter training mode
3. Switch IGN On within 5 sec
4. Switch IGN Off
5. Wait for 45-60 sec
6. Switch IGN On again
7. Wait for the double beep sound confirming successful training complete
8. Activate option with CopyKey service

Optional programming procedure for some trims:
1. Switch IGN Off for 45 sec
2. Push service button 14 times to enter training mode
3. Switch IGN On within 5 sec
4. Switch IGN Off
5. Wait for 45-60 sec
6. Switch IGN On 2nd time
7. Switch IGN Off
8. Wait for 45-60 sec
9. Switch IGN On 3rd time
10. Switch IGN Off
11. Wait for 45-60 sec
12. Switch IGN On 4th time
13. Wait for the double beep sound confirming successful training complete
14. Activate option with CopyKey service
